    "title": "Career Opportunity Store Manager at Big Bazaar",
    "description": "Big Bazaar invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Store Manager at our Vadodara location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Big Bazaar:\nBig Bazaar is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in CRM\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Big Bazaar!",
